data.description: 5% down financing OK at this breathtaking water views from every room of this two bedroom, two bathroom condo in East Fort Lauderdale. Spacious and well maintained the unit features large bay impact windows new tile floors, New AC, stainless steel, appliances, and walk in closets. Washer dryer in unit. Pool and Assigned parking spots. Boat docks available (waiting list) Bring your kayak or paddleboard and enjoy paradise. Association has full reserves. Seller to pay assessment which covers new roof and new sea wall.
